    "body": "Hi, [invoke](https://pypi.python.org/pypi/invoke/0.9.0) is the part of [fabric](https://pypi.python.org/pypi/Fabric/1.10.1) that only run local task. You can install install it with pip. \n\nThough you should not need it to build for local instal the css should be already bundled. \nIf you are just doing a local install you can probably do a `python setup.py symlink`, IIRC and  *nix only.\nand it should work. \n"
